channel.title: Server is online but not for me. Wtf
channel.description:
I was playing my server. I restarted it, I got logged out, I tried to log back in and I can't. Other people can. I didn't change anything client sided, and what I changed server-sided was removed. Then I restarted my computer. My IPv4 didn't change, I checked. Wth is wrong?
Some people are logged in, others can't log in.
[EDIT] I think I fixed it by doing nothing, not sure what I did, not sure what I did wrong... If you know how to fix this just tell me, thanks.
